Donate here as it will be beneficial as continous work and renovation are there and is done by donations by people.  Peaceful pace

featured_reviews.review_id:
Phusru station is in Bokaro district of Jharkhand. This station is not too big but as per the location is size is alright. This station contain some basic amenities like restroom, washroom and drinking water. This station is very close to subhash nagar, kargali and jawahar nagar areas. Bigger states like west bengal, madhyapradesh and Rajesthan are connected by this station. Passanger trains are also running in this route. And some of the big express is also running in this route like shaktipunj express. It's not too crowded station. Only few express and passenger train are running in this route. This station not contain lots of shops but only a few are there. Parking is also available outside.overall it's a very good station.
Location-5/5
Cleanliness-5/5
Maintaince-5/5
Amenities-4/5
Ambience-5/5
